OL,3,CChildren's hospital writes to families
OL,4,Cafter concerns raised over former
OL,5,Csurgeon
OL,7,FGreat Ormond Street Hospital has
OL,8,Fwritten to the families of all
OL,9,Fchildren treated by one of its former
OL,10,Fconsultant orthopaedic surgeons after
OL,11,Fconcerns were raised about his
OL,12,Fpractice.
OL,14,FThe trust has apologised for any
OL,15,F"worry and uncertainty" the letters
OL,16,Fabout the care provided by Yaser
OL,17,FJabbar may have caused.
