OL,3,CChildren's hospital writes to families
OL,4,Cafter concerns raised over former
OL,5,Csurgeon
OL,7,FMr Jabbar, who no longer works at the
OL,8,Fhospital, is reported to be an expert
OL,9,Fin limb reconstruction but has not had
OL,10,Fa licence to practise medicine in the
OL,11,FUK since January 8, according to the
OL,12,FGeneral Medical Council's website.
OL,14,FOne of the surgeon's former patients,
OL,15,Fwho is being represented by Hudgell
OL,16,FSolicitors, has been told they will be
OL,17,Fupdated on the review into Mr Jabbar's
OL,18,Fpractice in eight weeks.
