OL,3,CChildren's hospital writes to families
OL,4,Cafter concerns raised over former
OL,5,Csurgeon
OL,7,FThe hospital trust said the Royal
OL,8,FCollege of Surgeons (RCS) were asked
OL,9,Fto review its paediatric orthopaedic
OL,10,Fservice following concerns raised by
OL,11,Ffamily members and staff.
OL,13,FThe RCS then raised concerns about Mr
OL,14,FJabbar, which the trust said are being
OL,15,Ftaken "incredibly seriously" and will
OL,16,Fnow be reviewed by independent experts
OL,17,Ffrom other paediatric hospitals.
