OL,5,Csurgeon
OL,7,FThe GMC's website indicates the
OL,8,Forthopaedic surgeon was made the
OL,9,Fsubject of certain conditions on
OL,10,FJanuary 4 ` which included having a
OL,11,Fclinical supervisor at all times and
OL,12,Fseeking approval from the GMC before
OL,13,Fbeginning work in a non-NHS post or
OL,14,Fsetting.
OL,16,FA spokesman for Great Ormond Street
OL,17,Fsaid: "Following concerns raised by
OL,18,Ffamily members and our staff, we asked
OL,19,Fthe Royal College of Surgeons to
OL,20,Freview our paediatric orthopaedic
OL,21,Fservice.
