OL,3,CChildren's hospital writes to families
OL,4,Cafter concerns raised over former
OL,5,Csurgeon
OL,7,F"To date as part of the review, the
OL,8,FRCS has raised concerns around the
OL,9,Fpractice of a surgeon who no longer
OL,10,Fworks at the trust.
OL,12,F"We are taking these concerns
OL,13,Fincredibly seriously.
OL,15,F"We have written to all patients who
OL,16,Fmay have been impacted, and a group of
OL,17,Findependent experts from other
OL,18,Fpaediatric hospitals will review the
OL,19,Fcare of all the patients the surgeon
OL,20,Fwas involved in.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUwD@AOU
