OL,3,CChildren's hospital writes to families
OL,4,Cafter concerns raised over former
OL,5,Csurgeon
OL,7,F"We are sorry for the worry and
OL,8,Funcertainty this may cause the
OL,9,Ffamilies who are impacted.
OL,11,F"We are committed to learning from
OL,12,Fevery single patient that we treat,
OL,13,Fand to being open and transparent with
OL,14,Four families when care falls below the
OL,15,Fhigh standards we strive for."
OL,17,FCaroline Murgatroyd, of Hudgell
OL,18,FSolicitors, said: "We are currently
OL,19,Fsupporting a former patient and
OL,20,Finvestigating treatment provided to
OL,21,Fthem by Mr Jabbar.
