OL,3,CChildren's hospital writes to families
OL,4,Cafter concerns raised over former
OL,5,Csurgeon
OL,7,F"They have been contacted directly by
OL,8,Fthe trust to be informed of the review
OL,9,Fand assured that if any concerns are
OL,10,Fidentified with regards to their own
OL,11,Fcase, they will be informed as soon as
OL,12,Fpossible.
OL,14,F"We imagine other patients will have
OL,15,Fbeen contacted today too.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
