OL,3,CChildren's hospital writes to families
OL,4,Cafter concerns raised over former
OL,5,Csurgeon
OL,7,F"It is of course worrying when any
OL,8,Freview is launched into healthcare
OL,9,Fservices after concerns are raised,
OL,10,Fparticularly when those concerns are
OL,11,Fraised by surgeons themselves, and
OL,12,Frelate to the treatment of young
OL,13,Fchildren."
OL,15,FMs Murgatroyd continued: "However, in
OL,16,Four work we too often see concerns
OL,17,Fover treatment ignored and not acted
OL,18,Fupon, so whilst this will be worrying
OL,19,Ffor many people, we welcome the review.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@JO]wD@ZOU
