OL,3,CChildren's hospital writes to families
OL,4,Cafter concerns raised over former
OL,5,Csurgeon
OL,7,F"We also welcome the hospital's
OL,8,Fcommitment to ensuring the medical
OL,9,Frecords of other patients are now
OL,10,Findependently reviewed to check the
OL,11,Flevels of treatment provided.
OL,13,F"It will be a situation we watch with
OL,14,Finterest and hopefully one from which
OL,15,Fthe findings will be openly
OL,16,Fcommunicated with patients, and the
OL,17,Fwider public."
